{"tid":1564443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新華時評指香港經濟結構單一及地產獨大令社會矛盾不斷產生","createTime":"2019-09-12T18:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T18:48:48.000Z","uid":125193,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9a1e7c01fcf32d4966904358bd318c7e2bdd812c","tid":1564443,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T18:35:33.000Z","msg":"新華社發表時評，指出修例風波發展至今，折射出香港社會有深層次矛盾，極待解決，其中最突出、最迫切、最讓人詬病的是住屋問題。文章說香港經濟結構單一，地產經濟獨大，中小企失去生存空間，社會漸失活力，中產向下「淪陷」，青年難覓上升通道，貧富差距加大，令社會矛盾不斷產生。　<br />\n<br />\n文章指出特區政府亦意識到高樓價的危害，覓地加大供應量可謂對症下藥，但在反對派的掣肘下，進行得不順利。反對派的政治目的，不必再說，而一些既得利益集團的如意算盤，無非是以阻礙政府擴大土地供應、抬高自己囤積土地的價值，或改變土地用途，謀取最大利益。<br />\n<br />\n文章認為香港當務之急是止暴制亂，同時亦要採取有效措施，解決深層次矛盾，徹底消除社會動蕩的病根。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UWs4ksY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUWs4ksY.jpg&h=e3c8a3e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開始搞班有錢佬了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff47861ed3e7b3b25979129221e8d43505e081c0","tid":1564443,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T18:35:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"97e943377cc62a4c3cf5f09984f10c631b73ca62","tid":15